com.kinvey.persistence
Class KinveyUserImpl

java.lang.Object
  com.kinvey.persistence.EntityDict
      com.kinvey.persistence.KinveyUserImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
KinveyUser, Entity<EntityDict>, Persistable<EntityDict>
public class KinveyUserImpl
extends EntityDict
implements KinveyUser

The internal implementation of the KinveyUser interface. This class is not intended for external use.

The constructors of this class are intentionally protected. The public way to create a new user is via the KCSClient interface using the KCSClient.createUserWithUsername(String, String, KinveyCallback) method.
